channel.title: [PI] webclient error while loading
channel.description:
Im trying to make a webclient and my client.jar wont load it says this - same as webclient
i jsut found something out!t! this is before i jarred it - in my client there is a file called "raw" with it the client works and without it says the same error as the webclient...do i have to add this to the cache folder? i dont know at all what to do
Im trying to make a webclient and it looks like everything is loading perfect then while its loading it says
"Sorry, an error has occurred whilst loading cursedpkz. To fix this try the following(in order) 1.Close all browser windows and reloading - check, still not working 2.Try clearing cache - done, still not working 3.Try using different game world - I don't know if this even applies... 4.Try rebooting your computer - done, still broken 5.Try selecting a different version of Java from the play game menu"
use this url to see what i mean - http://cursedpkz.webs.com/webclient.htm
umm i have no idea how to fix this can some please help me !!!!!!!!! i will pay some1 if they can give me a working solution for this error or who can fix it for me with teamviewer
THIS IS THE TUT I FOLOWED - http://www.google.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/253018-how-make-your-project-insanity-client-webclient.html
